%description
Kendall random walks are a continuous-space Markov chains generated by the
Kendall generalized convolution. This package provides tools for
simulating these random walks and studying distributions related to them.
For more information about Kendall random walks see Jasiulis-Go≈Çdyn (2014)
<arXiv:1412.0220>.

